name: Sterling Protective Services Inc- Austin
tag_list: security-guards, security-officers, security-company, on-site-security, on-site-security-company, security-services, security-firm, body-guards, bodyguards, executive-protection, security-guard-service
overview:
Sterling Protective Services, Inc. offers on site security services and executive protection to the City of Austin and the surrounding cities. Our security guards and officers are background checked and highly trained, both in the classroom, and in the field.

Excelling in courtesy and communication, our security guards provide top quality service and meet the highest industry standards. In business since 1985, Sterling is proud to be one of the best security companies Austin has to offer.
